dct_title_s: Town plan of San Remo. G.S.G.S. 4380
dct_description_sm: Drawn and photolithographed at the War Office, 1943. 10-43. 104453. Military grid (brown). Grid provisional. Strategic buildings, law court and fascist headquarter are located. Includes index. AMS 2 United States. Army Map Service Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. no. 4380 In upper left margin: Italy 1:10,000. Air photographs have been used in the production of this plan." Strategic buildings, law court and fascist headquarter are located.
